00130 void CelFileDataTest::AddAlgorithmParametersTest()
00131 {
00132         ParameterNameValueType nvt;
00133         nvt.SetName(L"alpha1");
00134         nvt.SetValueFloat(0.004f);
00135         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_NO_THROW(cfMeta->AddAlgorithmParameter(nvt));
00136         
00137         // Check that the parameter
00138         ParameterNameValueTypeIt begin, end;
00139         cfMeta->GetFileHeader()->GetGenericDataHdr()->GetNameValIterators(begin, end);
00140         std::wstring parameterName = ALGORITHM_PARAM_NAME_PREFIX;
00141         parameterName += L"alpha1";
00142         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(begin->GetName() == parameterName);
00143 }

00145 void CelFileDataTest::GetAlgorithmParametersTest()
00146 {
00147         ParameterNameValueType nvt;
00148         nvt.SetName(L"alpha1");
00149         nvt.SetValueFloat(0.004f);
00150         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_NO_THROW(cfMeta->AddAlgorithmParameter(nvt));
00151         nvt.SetName(L"alpha2");
00152         nvt.SetValueFloat(0.06f);
00153         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_NO_THROW(cfMeta->AddAlgorithmParameter(nvt));
00154 
00155         ParameterNameValueTypeVector algParams;
00156         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_NO_THROW(cfMeta->GetAlgorithmParameters(algParams));
00157         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(algParams.size() == 2);
00158         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(algParams.at(0).GetName() == L"alpha1");
00159         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(algParams.at(1).GetName() == L"alpha2");
00160 }

00162 void CelFileDataTest::FindAlgorithmParameterTest()
00163 {
00164         ParameterNameValueType nvt;
00165         nvt.SetName(L"alpha1");
00166         nvt.SetValueFloat(0.004f);
00167         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_NO_THROW(cfMeta->AddAlgorithmParameter(nvt));
00168         nvt.SetName(L"alpha2");

00171
